# Dev-VM IP를 변수로 저장
@DEV_VM_IP=127.0.0.1
@DEV_VM_PORT=8000
@REQUEST_HEADER=http://{{DEV_VM_IP}}:{{DEV_VM_PORT}}

### VM 목록 조회 (GET)
GET {{REQUEST_HEADER}}/v1/vms HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### VM 생성 (POST)
POST {{REQUEST_HEADER}}/v1/vms HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "final-test-vm-02",
    "cpu": 1,
    "ram": 1024,
    "image_name": "Ubuntu-Base-22.04" 
}